item.title: About Me
item.description: Hi I’m Paul, I live near Düsseldorf, Germany. I am the founder of Tech-Doktor.de, an IT student and tech enthusiast. I’ve been building software since elementary school, so my love for computers and technology is lifelong. I’m interested in anything that will help me understand myself and others better. The best way to understand people is to understand the environment they have that shaped them. That’s why I’m also fascinated by psychology and the history of our species.
